mmend is to NOT think in terms of Kundalini and its rise. Just do sadhana, =
overcome your weaknesses and improve your detachment over time. Again, I wa=
nt to emphasize that detachment is not disgust or distaste for life/things/=
people around you. Disgust is the other side of coin of attachment. It is a=
 negative attachment.=C2=A0
