 or not. Worry about whether you are able to resist 6 internal enemies (sha=
dripus) and 8 bondages (ashta pashas) or not. If your ability to resist the=
m is increasing, you are making progress. EVEN IF your Kundalini is fast as=
leep, you are still making progress. When you completely overcome them, Kun=
dalini (your self-awareness) will automatically ascend to the top and meet =
Her Lord (true Self).
