ray to you and please give it to me", "I am scared of Kundalini rise, I wil=
l pray to you and please protect me" - all this is just a business deal. Th=
ere is something you want and you ask god for it. True surrender has no pla=
ce for agendas, desires, demands or expectations. True surrender is losing =
